{"tid":2177391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔係潮文」喺老母面前倒咗碗湯","createTime":"2020-08-27T16:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T05:01:10.000Z","uid":72497,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"046cbc53d01c3cf3de551bcddd982f4c231454af","tid":2177391,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"佢冇啦啦拎住碗湯入我房（我同朋友喺房傾緊計）問知唔知充電寶擺咗喺邊<br />\n<br />\n一聽到呢啲支語個人即時怒火攻心，心諗我啲朋友全撚部都深黃嚟㗎嘛，你講支語即係喺我朋友面前拆我台啫，一時火遮眼就倒咗碗湯<br />\n<br />\n依家冷靜返落嚟好後悔，好驚佢以後都唔再俾零花錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4810f1f4b03bfd439e6e61c5dd14fa07bd7d4d","tid":2177391,"uid":277186,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"已封鎖會員 子不離宮"},{"pid":"9d7eb638528b76565392745ff1e95f80ce1ab97a","tid":2177391,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:33:11.000Z","msg":"佢唔畀咪我畀囉"},{"pid":"8d288c4cf9c60ce42277a966c38842546f6d8e27","tid":2177391,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa0e60de7f3999a06c1d4a01420afba90a17e25","tid":2177391,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"be4810f1f4b03bfd439e6e61c5dd14fa07bd7d4d","tid":2177391,"uid":277186,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"已封鎖會員 子不離宮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"冇..你.."},{"pid":"a3df4be4ba60b57838d18b8e05c1eb39b9357744","tid":2177391,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d288c4cf9c60ce42277a966c38842546f6d8e27","tid":2177391,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"